flows.name: flows/test
flows.body:
id: test

inputs:
  stringValueSet:
    required: true
    type: STRING
    debugValue: "S, M, L"
  string:
    required: false
    type: STRING
    debugValue: "A"
  number:
    required: false
    type: INTEGER
    debugValue: "5"
  numberRange:
    required: true
    type: INTEGER
    debugValue: "5 - 10"

tasks:
  - numberCode:
      id: numberCode
      then: end
      decisionTable:
        ref: numberCode
        collection: false
        inputs:
          inputColumn: stringValueSet
